						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in front of the Rāmalingēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>1612 A.D.</p>						

						<p>It is dated in Śaka 1534, Parīdhāvi, Chaitra, śu. 2. corresponding to 1612 A.D. March 24, Tuesday.</p>						

						<p>Badly damaged and worn out. It seems to record the gift of <hi rend="italic">daśavanda</hi> land for the construction and maintanance of a tank.</p>						

						</summary>
